body_html: Fixed with 1c57936. The commit is very large since it bundled many changes, but the important change is in minimap.ts. Feel free to reopen if you run into this issue again. You won't see this fix before the next release unless you rebuild TensorBoard yourself following the instructions in https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tensorboard/README.md
